idare.metanode.internal.Interfaces

Class DataSetProperties

  • java.lang.Object
    • idare.metanode.internal.Interfaces.DataSetProperties
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbstractItemDataSetProperties

    public abstract class DataSetProperties
extends java.lang.Object
    Datasetproperties allow the use of a specific class of DataSets for multiple different layouts. The cotain information about localisation preferences and can provide different DataContainers (and thus layouts), for a single Class of DataSets.
    Author:
    Thomas Pfau
